<h1>Лохматые брови и неистовые глаза Эфроимсона. К 25-летию со дня смерти</h1>
<h2>С.С. Неретина</h2>
<p style="margin-left: 35.4pt; text-indent: 35.25pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">Аннотация: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">25 лет назад умер &laquo;неистовый&raquo; Эфроимсон, первый генетик человека, которого интересовала, помимо собственно профессиональных проблем, связанных с генетикой, проблема феномена гениальности, который он пытался объяснить с генетико-медицинских позиций.</span></p>  <p style="margin-left: 35.4pt; text-indent: 0cm" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>  <p style="margin-left: 35.4pt; text-indent: 35.25pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">Ключевые слова</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">репрессии, альтруизм, гений, подагра, туберкулез, синдром Марфана, синдром Морриса, генетика.</span></p>  <p style="margin-left: 35.4pt; text-indent: 0cm" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">&nbsp;</span><strong style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0cm; font-size: 0.8em"><span style="font-size: 18pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">Shaggy brows and fierce eyes of Efroymson</span></strong></p>  <p style="margin-left: 35.4pt; text-indent: 35.4pt" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><strong><em><span>Neretina S., Moscow</span></em></strong></p><p style="margin-left: 35.4pt; text-indent: 35.4pt" class="MsoNormal" align="left">&nbsp;<strong style="text-indent: 35.4pt; text-align: right; font-size: 0.8em"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">Abstract: </span></strong><span style="text-indent: 35.4pt; text-align: right; font-size: 0.8em">25 years ago died a &quot;violent&quot; Efroymson, the first man geneticist was interested in, in addition to the professional issues associated with genetics, the phenomenon of genius, which he tried to explain with genetic and medical positions</span><span style="text-indent: 35.4pt; text-align: right; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #222222">.</span><span style="font-size: 0.8em; text-indent: 0cm">&nbsp;</span></p>  <strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Key words: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Georgia, serif">repression, altruism, genius, gout, tuberculosis, Marfan syndrome, Morris syndrome, genetics.</span>	<p class="fullTextLink">
		<a href="https://vox-journal.org/content/vox17/Vox17-Neretina-Ef.pdf">Полный текст RU</a>
